description: Dutch police catch a suspect in a tight spot after being alerted to mobile phone thefts.
title: Man arrested with 30 phones in cycling shorts after rock gig
title_page: Man arrested with 30 phones in cycling shorts after rock gig - BBC News
maintext: It is not yet clear if the suspect - a Romanian national - had accomplices at the Canadian band's Amsterdam concert, which took place on 21 January.
